X open rc.conf with nvim
W # open the log window where can review messages that pop up at bottom
w # open task window. 可以查看当前正在运行的后台进程，比如拷贝
<C-c> stop the currently running background process, like copying files

yy # copy the selection. ("ya" to add files to the copy buffer, "yr" to remove files again, "yt" for toggling)

zh # set show hidden!
uv # unset the file selection

####### shell command
S # open a shell in the current directory
! # 快速执行shell命令
@ # 对当前选择的文件快速执行shell命令

####### tab related
gn, <C+n> # create a new tab
gc # close tab

####### Order by
oS # size reverse
oM # mtime reverse

dc # 得到文件夹的累计大小
vdcv # 显示当前目录下的所有文件夹大小

MH # linemode:size human readable, mtime

####### bookmark
um<key> # unset any bookmarks

####### Change the permissions of the selection.
<octal>=, +<who><what>, -<who><what>
777= # is equivalent to chmod 777 %s, 
+ar # does chmod a+r %s,
-ow # does chmod o-w %s etc.

####### chmod
+u{rwx} # 文件拥有者权限增加
-a{rwx} # 所有用户权限限制
